<subSubSection id="51E9E7B8D301AF4E66DE71E090BFD9C4" pageId="95" pageNumber="95" type="description">
<paragraph id="C6D089207DF746AD9D49DFA6469026E0" pageId="95" pageNumber="95">Worker. Length 2 1/2 lines.-Obscure dark-red-brown, with the antennal, mandibles, legs, margins of the segments of the abdomen and its apex, more or less ferruginous; the insect entirely covered with a fine silky pile, or bloom; the head, thorax, node and basal segment of the abdomen with scattered punctures; the thorax and node at their apex concavely truncate, the truncation smooth, the node oblong, rounded anteriorly.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
